column2: SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, z, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY z) as rownum2 FROM (SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, z, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY z) as rownum FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # AND z BETWEEN # AND # AND (survey = # or survey = #) AND bestObjID < > #) as t where t.rownum % # = # order by z
